## Risk Analysis
- **Correctness**: Different implementations may give different widths for same input
- **Maintenance**: Bug fixes must be applied to 3 places
- **Testing**: Test coverage fragmented across implementations
- **Layout**: Inconsistent widths could cause misaligned layouts

